TextEng: No I'm not. I'm <FirstName>. And who are you?
You noticed? Why don't you run along now, before the witch comes back.
Text: 눈치챘어? 마녀가 돌아오기 전에 어서 가.

TextEng: You just wait here. I'll be back.
You be pretty. What you name?
Me not hag. You go now, before witch come back.
Text: 나 마녀 아니야. 빨리 가, 마녀 돌아오기 전에.

TextEng: You no move. Me be back.
What did you discover about the Spirit?
Other druids have disappeared too. Do you know where they are?
Text: 다른 드루이드들도 사라졌어. 어디 있는지 알아?

TextEng: Why don't you tell me what happened to you?
You know what wrong with Spirit?
Me want know how you got caught.
Other druids gone too. You know where them be?
Text: 다른 드루이드들도 없어졌어. 어디 있는지 알아?

TextEng: Why would you seek the witch?
That certainly turned out to be a brilliant decision.
Why you think of witch?
That be stupid idea.
Did she recognize you or something?
Why would she stare at your face?
She know you face from before?
Text: 전에 네 얼굴 본 적 있어?

TextEng: Why she stare at you face?
Tell me what you've learned about the Spirit of the Wood.
Text: 숲의 정령에 대해 알아낸 거 말해줘.

TextEng: Do you know what happened to the other druids?
Text: 다른 드루이드들한테 무슨 일이 있었는지 알아?

TextEng: Do you need help escaping, or can you make it on your own?
Text: 탈출하는 데 도움이 필요해, 아니면 혼자 갈 수 있어?

TextEng: What you learn 'bout Spirit of Wood?
Where other druids go?
Me go now. You get out okay?
Text: 나 이제 가. 너 나갈 수 있어?

TextEng: Tell me more about this pool.
How do you think the Spirit would have reacted to you?
Text: 정령이 너한테 어떻게 반응했을 것 같아?

TextEng: Tell me 'bout pool.
What Spirit do if you talk?
Text: 네가 말 걸면 정령이 뭘 해?

TextEng: Why didn't you go into it?
What do you mean another realm?
You no go into pool?
What you mean other realm?
Do you have any suggestions of what I should do?
Text: 내가 뭘 해야 할지 조언해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: So how did you get down here?
Now what me do?
How you get down here?
Why don't you tell me your story?
You tell me what happen to you.
He sent me to rescue some druids. Are you one of them?
Text: 그가 드루이드들을 구하라고 보냈어. 너도 그중 하나야?

TextEng: I have met someone named Aawill. How do you know him?
Text: 아윌이라는 사람을 만났어. 어떻게 아는 사이야?

TextEng: Him tell me rescue druids. You be druid?
Text: 그가 드루이드들 구하라고 했어. 너 드루이드야?

TextEng: Me know him. How you know him?
Text: 나 그 사람 알아. 어떻게 아는 사이야?

TextEng: What are you doing here in the witch's house?
Text: 마녀 집에서 뭘 하고 있는 거야?

TextEng: What you do in this place with witch?
Me cure Spirit. You be safe now.
I cured the Spirit of the Wood, so you can rest easy now.
Text: 숲의 정령을 치료했어, 이제 안심해도 돼.

TextEng: Me kill Spirit, so you no need worry no more.
Text: 나 정령 죽였어, 이제 걱정 안 해도 돼.

TextEng: I had to kill the Spirit of the Wood, so you don't have to worry about it now.
Text: 숲의 정령을 죽여야 했어, 이제 걱정 안 해도 돼.

TextEng: What mean you think that?
What are you talking about?
Me glad you think like me.
I'm glad you see it my way.
So, you no be mad at me?
So, you're not mad at me?
